    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 <i>Medieval Monuments</i> 创作者包探索中世纪伟大的建筑成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与知名的《Crusader Kings III》模组作者 <strong><i>PiGu</i></strong> 合作打造，<i>Medieval Monuments</i> 为游戏带来 20 种全新、多元，且具有文化意义的名胜建物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315540/extras/fae6cfce4ff400a5f12b000513cfd2d5.poster.avif?t=1770209661\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315540/extras/fae6cfce4ff400a5f12b000513cfd2d5.webm?t=1770209661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315540/extras/fae6cfce4ff400a5f12b000513cfd2d5.mp4?t=1770209661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创作者包包含以下名胜：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巴塞隆納船坞站</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大吉斯卡拉堡垒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >克吕尼修道院</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >佛罗伦萨大教堂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约克城墙</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大马士革清真寺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大昭寺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瓦特堡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣乔治教堂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诺夫哥罗德亚大教堂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣温塞斯劳大教堂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维谢格拉德城堡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡鲁因大学</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凯鲁万蓄水池</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加纳宫殿</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡诺土垒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >金色城堡杰伊瑟尔梅尔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科纳克太阳神庙</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >索玛普利大寺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瓦塔比石窟</p></li></ul>",
